Class WorkflowSchedulerParentPanel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JPanel
            • org.kepler.workflowscheduler.gui.WorkflowSchedulerParentPanel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, TabPane, ScheduleChangeListenerInterface, SearchSchedulesWorkerListenerInterface, UploadingKARFileListenerInterface

    public class WorkflowSchedulerParentPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements TabPane, UploadingKARFileListenerInterface
    This class represents the right panel of the scheduler dialog object. It can show one panel of the two options - a JLabel which ask user to select a remote workflow and a real scheduler panel.
    Author:
    tao
